{{作品名稱|name=''A Million Ways to Die in the West''|hk=奪命西|tw=百萬種硬的方式|cn=西部的一百万种死法}}是一部2014年[[塞思·麦克法兰|塞思·麦克法兰]]执导的美国喜剧西部片，[[塞思·麥克法蘭|塞思·麥克法蘭]]、[[Alec_Sulkin|Alec Sulkin]]和[[Wellesley_Wild|Wellesley Wild]]编剧。[[Media_Rights_Capital|Media Rights Capital]]制作，[[环球影业|环球影业]]发行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mrcstudios.com/film/14|accessdate=May 9, 2013|title=Media Rights Capital|archive-date=2016-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313125350/http://mrcstudios.com/film/14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Collura|first=Scott|title=Sarah Silverman for MacFarlane's A Million Ways to Die in the West|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/03/18/sarah-silverman-joining-macfarlanes-a-million-ways-to-die-in-the-west|work=IGN|accessdate=May 9, 2013|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322153418/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/03/18/sarah-silverman-joining-macfarlanes-a-million-ways-to-die-in-the-west|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[塞思·麥克法蘭|塞思·麥克法蘭]]、[[查理兹·塞隆|查理兹·塞隆]]、[[連恩·尼遜|連恩·尼遜]]、[[阿曼達·西耶弗里德|阿曼達·西耶弗里德]]、[[乔瓦尼·瑞比西|乔瓦尼·瑞比西]]、[[莎拉·席爾蔓|莎拉·席爾蔓]]和[[尼爾·柏德烈·夏里斯|尼爾·柏德烈·夏里斯]]主演。美国于2014年5月30日上映。<ref>{{cite web |last=Barrett |first=Annie |url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/05/10/a-million-ways-to-die-in-the-west-release/ |title='A Million Ways to Die in the West' gets summer 2014 release date | Inside Movies | EW.com |publisher=Insidemovies.ew.com |date= |accessdate=May 11, 2013 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006070556/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/05/10/a-million-ways-to-die-in-the-west-release/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |newspaper=Vulture |url=http://www.vulture.com/2013/05/neil-patrick-harris-joins-macfarlanes-western.html |title=Neil Patrick Harris Joins Seth MacFarlane’s A Million Ways to Die in the West |first=Jesse David |last=Fox |date=May 11, 2013 |accessdate=2014-05-26 |archive-date=2013-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110114140/http://www.vulture.com/2013/05/neil-patri